name: Come with me
description:
I will try to make the sun shine brighter for you
I'll even play dumb if it makes you smile
I will try to make you laugh if there are tears in your eyes
After all is said
After all is done
I will always be with you

Come with me, close your eyes
Hold my hand, calm down everything will be fine
Don't be afraid, we'll go through it all together
Raise your head and see tomorrow will be more beautiful
